data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Tucked away inside the gates of the coveted Talamore community in Watergrass, this  sprawling, 2-story, 3,475 sq. ft. home awaits. This floor plan truly is built for flexibility and  privacy, featuring 5 bedrooms, 4.5 baths, multiple ensuites, and a bonus room. Delight in  entertaining, the 22x19 living room offers luxury vinyl flooring, double tray ceilings, crown  molding, and triple sliding doors. It opens up beautifully to the expansive chef’s kitchen and  spacious dining room, creating a comfortable, easy flow in the main living areas. The 2 tone  kitchen is nicely appointed with granite countertops, a massive island with breakfast bar  seating, a built-in double oven, a cooktop, an eye-catching backsplash, a pantry, and much  more. The first floor also provides the owner’s suite, a half bath for guests, a laundry area, and  a second bedroom with a full ensuite bathroom. The owner’s suite is true to its name, featuring  a large walk-in closet and a stunning bathroom with abundant natural light, a central soaking  tub, dual sinks and vanity, and 2 entry walk-in shower. Upstairs you will find 3 more bedrooms,  one with an ensuite bathroom, a full guest bathroom, and a 15x18 bonus room. Watergrass is a  one-of-a-kind community centrally located in Wesley Chapel. It offers its own elementary  school, firehouse, and excellent top-notch amenities, including a resort-style pool, playground,  basketball court, tennis court, and more!! Don’t wait for new construction; give us a call today  to view this move-in-ready, like-new home.
